c: 5
v: 117
t: "“Nta kindi nababwiye uretse ibyo wantegetse (ko mbabwira nti) ‘Nimusenge Allah, Nyagasani wanjye akaba na Nyagasani wanyu. Kandi nari umuhamya wabo mu gihe cyose nari kumwe na bo, ariko ubwo wanzamuraga iwawe, ni Wowe wari Umugenzuzi wabo. Kandi Wowe uri Umuhamya uhebuje wa buri kintu.”"